00:38:33,700 --> 00:38:34,580
By wearing it,

586
00:38:34,660 --> 00:38:36,820
you'll be a super-duper great universe.

587
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:37,980
You won't be scared of anything.

588
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:40,900
How is it?

589
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:42,740
Does it look nice?

590
00:38:49,020 --> 00:38:49,860
Cover it.

591
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:52,780
Make sure it doesn't
get soaked in the rain.

592
00:38:55,980 --> 00:38:56,860
Thank you.

593
00:38:58,060 --> 00:38:59,940
This is the best gift I've ever received.

594
00:39:02,380 --> 00:39:03,020
You're welcome.

595
00:39:09,220 --> 00:39:09,860
Are you okay?

596
00:39:12,660 --> 00:39:13,300
I'm fine.

