00:39:46,300 --> 00:39:47,300
We're considered

601
00:39:48,140 --> 00:39:49,660
partners who've been
through adversity together.

602
00:39:53,020 --> 00:39:54,180
We'll definitely get out.

603
00:39:55,300 --> 00:39:56,220
It's just a matter of time.

604
00:39:56,980 --> 00:39:57,740
Fu Yunshen.

605
00:40:00,260 --> 00:40:01,940
I also have a present for you.

606
00:40:02,260 --> 00:40:03,140
What is it?

607
00:40:13,980 --> 00:40:14,660
Zhu Jiu.

608
00:40:15,420 --> 00:40:17,580
How dare you
hide such a good thing from me?

609
00:40:19,940 --> 00:40:21,980
