612
00:40:26,540 --> 00:40:28,060
Are you sure it would've been eaten?

613
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:29,460
Am I that stingy?

614
00:40:30,180 --> 00:40:31,380
Do I look like a chowhound?

615
00:40:56,020 --> 00:40:56,580
Eat it.

616
00:40:57,100 --> 00:40:58,260
I wanted to give it to you.

617
00:41:28,420 --> 00:41:29,060
Zhu Jiu.

618
00:41:35,460 --> 00:41:35,980
Zhu Jiu.

619
00:42:12,060 --> 00:42:12,580
Zhu Jiu.

620
00:43:14,100 --> 00:43:17,700
♪I see you in a dark corner♪

621
00:43:17,980 --> 00:43:21,340
♪With vulnerability overwhelming you♪

622
00:43:21,580 --> 00:43:23,660
♪Biting your lips
and facing away from me♪

623
00:43:23,900 --> 00:43:27,900
♪You break the walls of stubbornness♪

624
00:43:28,740 --> 00:43:31,700
♪Once more, another sundown
swiftly passes by♪

625
00:43:31,980 --> 00:43:37,140
♪Love is like a lie at the end
of the century♪

626
00:43:37,300 --> 00:43:43,060
♪That almost fools me♪

627
00:43:52,940 --> 00:43:59,540
♪A kiss can heal this wrecked world♪

628
00:43:59,860 --> 00:44:06,500
♪If there is a slight possibility
of avoiding loneliness♪

629
00:44:06,780 --> 00:44:13,180
♪Let me endure the heavy rainfall
with you♪

630
00:44:13,460 --> 00:44:17,500
♪If there is a slight possibility♪

631
00:44:17,740 --> 00:44:23,620
♪The moon that once shone for me
should stay radiate♪

632
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:29,740
♪You'll regain happiness
when you are true to yourself♪

633
00:44:39,220 --> 00:44:46,180
♪You feel my pain♪

634
00:44:46,300 --> 00:44:53,260
♪No reason for those meaningless winds
to pass by me♪

635
00:44:53,500 --> 00:45:00,180
♪When the meaningless things hit me♪

636
00:45:08,060 --> 00:45:14,540
♪Why must we miss out on each other
when our hearts are broken?♪

637
00:45:15,220 --> 00:45:21,820
♪Imitating others who flinch and escape
after love sparks fade away♪

638
00:45:21,980 --> 00:45:30,820
♪All I yearn for is the warmth deep within you♪
